headline: PayPal Holdings (NasdaqGS:PYPL) Partners With TerraPay For Real-Time Transfers In Middle East Africa
summary: PayPal Holdings (NasdaqGS:PYPL) experienced a 6.39% price increase last week, coinciding with the announcement of a partnership with TerraPay to bolster real-time fund transfers in the Middle East and Africa. This aligns with a broader market trend where tech stocks led U.S. indices higher amid easing trade tensions with China.
